{"type":null,"faqId":12908,"title":"P7 无法使用闪光灯，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请切换闪光灯模式为强制闪光灯模式</span><span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，拍照或录像时将始终打开闪光灯。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若开启了闪光灯自动模式</span><span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，相机将会根据环境光强度自动开启或关闭闪光灯。若要在光线充足的环境下使用闪光灯，请开启强制闪光灯模式。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>请确认手机电池电量是否充足。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>为延长手机的使用时间，当电池电量过低时，系统会自动禁止使用闪光灯。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>为保证手机正常使用，请及时为手机充电。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>手机过热或闪光灯使用过于频繁，导致闪光灯温度过高时可能无法使用闪光灯，请过一段时间后重试。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":2,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3831","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1400142230000,"seriesProductName":"Sophia-L00,Sophia-L05,Sophia-L07,Sophia-L09","visitedTimes":764,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"P7","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}